<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<!-- 1. Google Search Console ka Code -->
    <meta name="google-site-verification" content="gI0wc2XiDKXyDpX7Kmf3Y2xEakvFer_i1fw6gBz7SW4" />

    <!-- 2. Tumhari Website ka Description (Jo baad me badal bhi sakte ho) -->
    <meta name="description" content="VidhyaLitee - Digitalise your school with VidhyaLitee. India's smartest all-in-one school management ERP designed to automate attendance, streamline payments, and transform school administration into a paperless system.">

    <title>VidhyaLitee | Digital School Management System</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #2563eb;
            --primary-dark: #1d4ed8;
            --dark: #1e293b;
            --light: #f8fafc;
            --accent: #3b82f6;
            --navy: #1e3c72;
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background: var(--light);
            color: var(--dark);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* ---------- HERO SECTION ---------- */
        .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f2444 0%, #1e3c72 55%, #2a5298 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 110px 20px 80px;
            text-align: center;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -30%;
            left: -5%;
            width: 50%;
            height: 160%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59,130,246,0.13) 0%, transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            background: rgba(59,130,246,0.18);
            border: 1px solid rgba(96,165,250,0.3);
            color: #93c5fd;
            padding: 7px 18px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 26px;
        }

        .hero-section h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 7vw, 3.6rem);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1.15;
        }

        .hero-section h1 span { color: #60a5fa; }

        .hero-section > p {
            font-size: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.2rem);
            opacity: 0.88;
            max-width: 680px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
        }

        .hero-btns {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 70px;
        }

        .cta-btn {
            padding: 14px 32px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: #fff;
            color: #1e3c72;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.22);
        }

        .download-btn {
            background: transparent;
            color: white;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
        }

        .download-btn:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        /* ---------- APP PREVIEW / SCREENSHOTS ---------- */
        .preview-section {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0f2444 0%, #f8fafc 40%);
            padding: 0 20px 80px;
        }

        .preview-wrapper {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 24px;
            align-items: start;
        }

        .preview-card {
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease;
            background: #fff;
        }

        .preview-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.01);
            box-shadow: 0 35px 80px rgba(37,99,235,0.25);
        }

        .preview-card img {
            width: 100%;
            display: block;
            border-radius: 20px;
        }

        .preview-card-label {
            padding: 14px 18px;
            background: #fff;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #475569;
        }

        .preview-card-label i {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        /* ---------- COLLAGE + SS STRIP ---------- */
        .collage-wrapper {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto 28px;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .collage-card {
            border-radius: 22px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            transition: transform 0.4s ease;
        }

        .collage-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px) scale(1.01);
        }

        .collage-card img {
            width: 100%;
            display: block;
        }

        .ss-strip {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 18px;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .ss-card {
            border-radius: 14px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.22);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            background: #fff;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .ss-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(37,99,235,0.25);
        }

        .ss-card img {
            width: 100%;
            display: block;
            border-radius: 14px 14px 0 0;
        }

        .ss-label {
            padding: 10px 14px;
            background: #fff;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #475569;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 7px;
        }

        .ss-label i { color: var(--primary); font-size: 13px; }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .ss-strip { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }

        /* ---------- STATS STRIP ---------- */
        .stats-strip {
            background: var(--primary);
            padding: 50px 5%;
        }

        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-item {
            color: white;
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 2.6rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            opacity: 0.85;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* ---------- FEATURES GRID ---------- */
        .features-section {
            padding: 90px 5%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .section-head {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 55px;
        }

        .section-head .tag {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            display: block;
        }

        .section-head h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .section-head p {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 1rem;
            max-width: 580px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 38px 32px;
            border-radius: 22px;
            text-align: left;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(37,99,235,0.1);
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }

        .feature-card .icon-wrap {
            width: 68px;
            height: 68px;
            background: #eff6ff;
            border-radius: 18px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 22px;
        }

        .feature-card .icon-wrap i {
            font-size: 1.7rem;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 0.93rem;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .feature-card .card-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 18px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--primary);
            background: #eff6ff;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }

        
        /* ---------- DOCUMENT GENERATION SECTION ---------- */
        .docs-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72 0%, #2a5298 100%);
            padding: 90px 5%;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .docs-section .section-head h2 { color: white; }
        .docs-section .section-head p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); }
        .docs-section .section-head .tag { color: #93c5fd; }

        .docs-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 22px;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto 50px;
        }

        .doc-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 32px 24px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .doc-card:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            border-color: rgba(96,165,250,0.5);
        }

        .doc-card .doc-icon {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            color: #93c5fd;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            display: block;
        }

        .doc-card h4 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: white;
        }

        .doc-card p {
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
            line-height: 1.55;
        }

        /* ---------- CHART PREVIEW SECTION ---------- */
        .charts-section {
            padding: 90px 5%;
            background: white;
        }

        .charts-layout {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 50px;
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .charts-text h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.3rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .charts-text p {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 0.97rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .charts-list {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 14px;
        }

        .charts-list li {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #334155;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .charts-list li i {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 1rem;
            width: 20px;
        }

        .charts-img {
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(37,99,235,0.15);
        }

        .charts-img img {
            width: 100%;
            display: block;
        }

        @media (max-width: 750px) {
            .charts-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }

        /* ---------- CTA SECTION ---------- */
        .final-cta {
            background: #f0f5ff;
            padding: 90px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .final-cta h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--dark);
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }

        .final-cta p {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 36px;
        }

        .final-btns {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn-blue {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 34px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .btn-blue:hover {
            background: var(--primary-dark);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(37,99,235,0.3);
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--dark);
            border: 2px solid #cbd5e1;
            padding: 14px 34px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .btn-outline:hover {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            color: var(--primary);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .hero-section { padding: 80px 16px 60px; }
            .features-section { padding: 60px 4%; }
            .doc-card { padding: 24px 18px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include("partials/HomePageNavbar") %>

    <!-- ── HERO ───────────────────────────────── -->
    <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="hero-badge">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i> India's Smartest School ERP
        </div>
        <h1>VidhyaLitee: The <span>Future</span> of<br>School Management</h1>
        <p>Automate attendance, simplify fee collection, generate marksheets & certificates — all from one powerful dashboard.</p>
        <div class="hero-btns">
            <a href="/login" class="cta-btn btn-primary">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-rocket"></i> Get Started Now
            </a>
            <a href="/downloads/SchoolApp.apk" class="cta-btn download-btn" download>
                <i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen-button"></i> Download App
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── APP PREVIEW SCREENSHOTS ───────────── -->
    <div class="preview-section">
        <!-- Main collage -->
        <div class="collage-wrapper">
            <div class="collage-card">
                <img src="/images/app_collage.png" alt="VidhyaLitee App Preview — Dashboard, Charts, Fees, Teachers">
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Individual screenshot strip -->
        <div class="ss-strip">
            <div class="ss-card">
                <img src="/images/ss_dashboard.png" alt="Admin Dashboard">
                <div class="ss-label"><i class="fa-solid fa-house-chimney"></i> Admin Dashboard</div>
            </div>
            <div class="ss-card">
                <img src="/images/ss_fees.png" alt="Fees Collection">
                <div class="ss-label"><i class="fa-solid fa-credit-card"></i> Fees Collection</div>
            </div>
            <div class="ss-card">
                <img src="/images/ss_teachers.png" alt="Teachers Management">
                <div class="ss-label"><i class="fa-solid fa-chalkboard-teacher"></i> Teachers List</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── STATS STRIP ────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="stats-strip">
        <div class="stats-grid">
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-number">50+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Schools Using VidhyaLitee</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-number">25,000+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Students Managed</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-number">99.9%</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Uptime Guaranteed</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-item">
                <div class="stat-number">₹2Cr+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Fees Collected Online</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── FEATURE CARDS ──────────────────────── -->
    <div class="features-section">
        <div class="section-head">
            <span class="tag">What We Offer</span>
            <h2>Everything Your School Needs</h2>
            <p>From daily attendance to online fee collection — VidhyaLitee handles it all, beautifully.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon-wrap"><i class="fa-solid fa-credit-card"></i></div>
                <h3>Smart Fee Payment</h3>
                <p>Integrated Razorpay for seamless and secure online fee collection with automated receipts and pending due tracking.</p>
                <span class="card-tag">Razorpay Integrated</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon-wrap"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-check"></i></div>
                <h3>Attendance Tracking</h3>
                <p>Track daily attendance of students and staff. View beautiful pie charts and monthly real-time reports in one click.</p>
                <span class="card-tag">Real-time Reports</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon-wrap"><i class="fa-solid fa-bullhorn"></i></div>
                <h3>Instant Notices</h3>
                <p>Send important announcements and digital circulars to parents and staff in seconds. No paper, no delays.</p>
                <span class="card-tag">Push Notifications</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon-wrap"><i class="fa-solid fa-file-invoice"></i></div>
                <h3>Marksheet Generation</h3>
                <p>Generate professional marksheets/report cards as PDFs with subject-wise marks, grades, and school branding.</p>
                <span class="card-tag">PDF Export</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon-wrap"><i class="fa-solid fa-id-card"></i></div>
                <h3>Admit Card Generator</h3>
                <p>Create and issue exam admit cards instantly for each student with roll number, exam schedule, and photo.</p>
                <span class="card-tag">Exam Ready</span>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="icon-wrap"><i class="fa-solid fa-graduation-cap"></i></div>
                <h3>TC & Bonafide Certificates</h3>
                <p>Generate Transfer Certificates and Bonafide certificates with a single click. Formal, printable, professional.</p>
                <span class="card-tag">Official Documents</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── DOCUMENT GENERATION SECTION ──────── -->
    <div class="docs-section">
        <div class="section-head">
            <span class="tag">Document Generation</span>
            <h2>Professional Documents in One Click</h2>
            <p>Marksheets, Transfer Certificates, Admit Cards, and Bonafide Certificates — all instantly generated as PDFs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="docs-grid">
            <div class="doc-card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-file-invoice doc-icon"></i>
                <h4>Marksheet / Report Card</h4>
                <p>Subject-wise marks, grades, total, percentage, result status — all in a professionally designed layout.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="doc-card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-right-from-bracket doc-icon"></i>
                <h4>Transfer Certificate (TC)</h4>
                <p>Instant TC generation with school seal, student details, and formal formatting. Ready to print.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="doc-card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-id-badge doc-icon"></i>
                <h4>Admit Card</h4>
                <p>Exam admit cards with student photo, roll number, exam schedule, and subject details.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="doc-card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-certificate doc-icon"></i>
                <h4>Bonafide Certificate</h4>
                <p>Issue bonafide certificates on-demand for bank, scholarship, or other official purposes.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── CHARTS / ANALYTICS SECTION ────────── -->
    <div class="charts-section">
        <div class="charts-layout">
            <div class="charts-text">
                <h2>Powerful Analytics at a Glance</h2>
                <p>VidhyaLitee's dashboard gives you real-time insights through beautiful charts and reports — so you always know what's happening at your school.</p>
                <ul class="charts-list">
                    <li><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-pie"></i> Student attendance pie chart — daily & monthly</li>
                    <li><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-bar"></i> Fee collection bar graphs — month-wise</li>
                    <li><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line"></i> Academic performance trend lines</li>
                    <li><i class="fa-solid fa-table-columns"></i> Class-wise and student-wise breakdown</li>
                    <li><i class="fa-solid fa-rupee-sign"></i> Expense vs income financial reports</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="charts-img">
                <img src="/images/ss_charts.png" alt="Revenue & Expenses Pie Charts — VidhyaLitee Analytics Dashboard">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── FINAL CTA ───────────────────────────── -->
    <div class="final-cta">
        <h2>Ready to Digitalise Your School?</h2>
        <p>Join 50+ schools already using VidhyaLitee. Get started in minutes — no setup fee.</p>
        <div class="final-btns">
            <a href="/login" class="btn-blue"><i class="fa-solid fa-rocket"></i> Get Started Now</a>
            <a href="/features" class="btn-outline"><i class="fa-solid fa-list-check"></i> See All Features</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include("partials/HomePageFooter") %>
    <script src="/backButton.js"></script>
</body>

</html>